citations:
    citation-asos-appendix:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Appendix"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "A Storm of Swords appendix — house listings reflecting state of affairs at the start of Book 3. Key changes from ACOK: Stevron Frey died after Oxcross, Joffrey now King on Iron Throne, Robb is King in the North and King of the Trident, Stannis styled rebel, Renly confirmed dead, Tyrion wounded at Blackwater."
